    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 (not-assessed) per the MRL 2 credibility matrix in ASME V&V 40-2018. Discretization error factor exceeds requirement (achieved Gradation 3 vs. required Gradation 2), providing additional confidence. Validation against FDA benchmark dataset demonstrates NIH prediction within ±15% acceptance band at all five operating points. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Decision: Accepted for 510(k) submission support.",
